# Git Rules

- This repo (DenchHQ/DenchClaw) is a **fork** of openclaw/openclaw.
- When creating PRs, ALWAYS target `DenchHQ/DenchClaw` — never the upstream `openclaw/openclaw`.
  Use `gh pr create --repo DenchHQ/DenchClaw` to ensure this.
- NEVER commit or push without explicit user approval.
- NEVER force push to main/master.
